1
00:01:25,370 --> 00:01:32,000
[Echoes of a Thousand Moons]

2
00:01:32,060 --> 00:01:34,960
[Episode 4]

3
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:39,910
Brigade Commander

4
00:01:40,150 --> 00:01:41,410
gave a one-word order—

5
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,509
"Die."

6
00:01:43,310 --> 00:01:44,440
Then we die.

7
00:01:51,410 --> 00:01:52,390
Brothers!

8
00:01:52,590 --> 00:01:53,640
Yes!

9
00:01:57,620 --> 00:01:58,840
Move out!

10
00:02:26,190 --> 00:02:35,220
[Command Postof Division Headquarters ]

11
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:29,800
-Yes.
-Division Commander

12
00:02:30,250 --> 00:02:31,400
I will execute the order immediately.

13
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,600
Division Commander!

14
00:02:35,660 --> 00:02:37,590
Do you know that the 159th Division

15
00:02:37,640 --> 00:02:39,240
has withdrawn from Liu Town?

16
00:02:40,300 --> 00:02:41,490
I just found out.

17
00:02:41,700 --> 00:02:42,660
Why?

18
00:02:43,230 --> 00:02:44,100
Whose order was that?

19
00:02:44,100 --> 00:02:45,910
Who do you think

20
00:02:46,470 --> 00:02:48,140
could bypass the Theater Command,

21
00:02:48,140 --> 00:02:50,270
the Army Group, and the Army Commander

22
00:02:50,620 --> 00:02:51,960
and redeploy an entire division?

23
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:53,190
The Chairman?

24
00:02:56,410 --> 00:02:57,770
We can retreat too.

25
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:59,180
We can retreat?

26
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:00,790
What about the 87th Brigade?

27
00:03:00,790 --> 00:03:02,350
We can't reach them by phone now.

28
00:03:02,350 --> 00:03:03,390
There's no time

29
00:03:03,420 --> 00:03:04,280
to send a messenger.

30
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:05,340
We should at least dispatch a regiment

31
00:03:05,340 --> 00:03:06,870
to cover their withdrawal.

32
00:03:07,570 --> 00:03:08,720
Since there's no time,

33
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:10,230
then let them

34
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:14,880
cover the withdrawal

35
00:03:15,190 --> 00:03:17,450
of the division's main force
and the army at large,

36
00:03:17,450 --> 00:03:19,410
securing the flank and rear.

37
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:21,270
Division Commander, let me take my men.

38
00:03:21,270 --> 00:03:23,070
Orders from the Army Commander—

39
00:03:24,829 --> 00:03:26,160
withdraw immediately.

40
00:04:06,650 --> 00:04:08,170
Hey, Nishida!

41
00:04:08,700 --> 00:04:10,590
What are you staring at?

42
00:04:12,330 --> 00:04:14,520
This damp air

43
00:04:14,550 --> 00:04:17,100
mixed with wood smoke

44
00:04:17,130 --> 00:04:20,269
smells downright foul.

45
00:06:05,950 --> 00:06:07,750
It feels like someone's coming.

46
00:09:36,890 --> 00:09:37,790
-Freeze!
-Freeze!

47
00:09:37,790 --> 00:09:38,390
Don't!

48
00:09:38,390 --> 00:09:40,090
Don't! Don't! Don't!

49
00:09:42,970 --> 00:09:44,090
Kong Erbao?

50
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,560
Platoon Leader Wang.

51
00:09:46,260 --> 00:09:47,650
What the hell? It's you.

52
00:10:02,450 --> 00:10:03,170
Get up!

53
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:06,630
What happened?

54
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:07,870
I...

55
00:10:13,330 --> 00:10:14,970
Erbao, you're back?

56
00:10:16,610 --> 00:10:18,100
I finally found you.

57
00:10:18,170 --> 00:10:20,100
Which direction did you come from?

58
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:23,470
I... I passed a village.

59
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:25,050
There is an arch bridge,

60
00:10:25,150 --> 00:10:26,120
covered in corpses.

61
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:27,480
I crawled over the corpses,

62
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,680
and found you.

63
00:10:29,140 --> 00:10:30,470
The Little Tang bridge?

64
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:32,900
You got lost?

65
00:10:32,930 --> 00:10:33,680
No.

66
00:10:33,870 --> 00:10:34,910
You said

67
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,510
wherever you go, I follow.

68
00:10:36,780 --> 00:10:38,030
Blindy said I'm lucky.

69
00:10:38,030 --> 00:10:39,290
As long as I follow you,

70
00:10:39,390 --> 00:10:40,720
the bombs won't hit you.

71
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:43,450
You want to return to the squad?

72
00:10:43,590 --> 00:10:45,990
Wherever the Brigade Commander goes, I go!

73
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:49,010
Good brother.

74
00:10:49,090 --> 00:10:49,850
Loyal.

75
00:10:50,170 --> 00:10:50,880
I knew it.

76
00:10:50,910 --> 00:10:52,240
You'd never abandon us.

77
00:10:53,030 --> 00:10:53,600
Kong Erbao!

78
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:54,170
Here!

79
00:10:54,500 --> 00:10:55,000
Rejoin the squad!

80
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:55,720
Yes, sir!

81
00:10:56,550 --> 00:10:57,360
Move out!

82
00:10:59,210 --> 00:11:01,530
Did you hurt yourself
when you fell just now?

83
00:11:01,530 --> 00:11:02,530
You're loyal.

84
00:11:02,560 --> 00:11:04,490
I knew you were this kind of person.

85
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:06,200
Good brother.

86
00:11:06,300 --> 00:11:07,070
Good brother.

87
00:11:07,070 --> 00:11:08,080
Let's go.

88
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:12,210
Fear not the lack of armor,
for my cloak is yours to share.

89
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:14,740
Not bad.

90
00:11:22,680 --> 00:11:28,750
[Liu Town]

91
00:11:42,310 --> 00:11:43,240
Company Commander Ye!

92
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:43,550
Yes!

93
00:11:43,550 --> 00:11:45,440
Take two men and scout
the outskirts of the town.

94
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:46,040
Yes, sir!

95
00:11:46,400 --> 00:11:46,890
Follow me.

96
00:11:46,890 --> 00:11:47,490
Yes, sir.

97
00:11:48,740 --> 00:11:49,170
Platoon Leader Wang!

98
00:11:49,170 --> 00:11:49,810
Yes!

99
00:11:49,840 --> 00:11:50,930
Go check inside the town

100
00:11:50,930 --> 00:11:52,290
and see if there are
any of our allied forces left.

101
00:11:52,290 --> 00:11:53,010
Yes, sir!

102
00:11:53,190 --> 00:11:53,900
Follow me!

103
00:11:56,410 --> 00:11:57,730
Keep a sharp lookout.

104
00:12:12,870 --> 00:12:13,840
What did you find?

105
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:15,330
The town is completely empty.

106
00:12:15,330 --> 00:12:17,590
There are no allied forces to support us.

107
00:12:40,910 --> 00:12:42,840
The 159th Division has retreated.

108
00:12:47,510 --> 00:12:48,060
How is it?

109
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:49,240
Brigade Commander,

110
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:50,600
To the northeast,
we've the spotted the Japanese Army—

111
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:51,840
infantry and tanks.

112
00:12:51,930 --> 00:12:52,730
Report!

113
00:12:54,200 --> 00:12:54,900
Report!

114
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:57,360
Brigade Commander,

115
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:59,490
the road we came from
is full of the Japanese Army.

116
00:12:59,490 --> 00:13:00,520
We can't go back.

117
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:10,960
If the higher-ups

118
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:13,270
aren't just ordering
the 159th Division to withdraw,

119
00:13:13,270 --> 00:13:15,030
then we fight the Japanese here!

120
00:13:15,030 --> 00:13:15,690
This way,

121
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:17,750
we can at least buy more time

122
00:13:17,750 --> 00:13:19,750
for our brothers at home to retreat.

123
00:13:20,240 --> 00:13:21,240
What do you say?

124
00:13:21,270 --> 00:13:22,480
Okay!

125
00:13:24,490 --> 00:13:25,890
When the Japanese fight,

126
00:13:25,990 --> 00:13:28,150
it's always artillery bombardment first,
then tanks charge,

127
00:13:28,150 --> 00:13:29,410
and infantry follows.

128
00:13:29,410 --> 00:13:31,480
So let them in before we strike.

129
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:32,470
Staff Officer Xie!

130
00:13:32,470 --> 00:13:33,030
Yes!

131
00:13:33,120 --> 00:13:34,240
Take 15 men

132
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:35,960
and set up defenses
in the western part of the town.

133
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:36,630
Yes, sir!

134
00:13:36,990 --> 00:13:37,670
Follow me!

135
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:40,840
Company Commander Ye!

136
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:41,240
Yes!

137
00:13:41,270 --> 00:13:42,100
Take 10 men

138
00:13:42,150 --> 00:13:43,410
and hide on both sides of the road

139
00:13:43,410 --> 00:13:44,390
to specifically deal with the tanks.

140
00:13:44,390 --> 00:13:44,950
Yes, sir!

141
00:13:46,080 --> 00:13:47,140
Collect grenades!

142
00:13:49,940 --> 00:13:50,660
Ready?

143
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:51,750
Ready.

144
00:13:51,850 --> 00:13:52,780
Follow me.

145
00:13:58,150 --> 00:13:58,870
Platoon Leader Wang!

146
00:13:58,870 --> 00:13:59,320
Yes!

147
00:13:59,370 --> 00:14:00,550
You're in charge of
cutting off all communication

148
00:14:00,550 --> 00:14:02,120
between the enemy infantry and tanks
from the flank.

149
00:14:02,120 --> 00:14:02,950
Yes, sir!

150
00:14:03,100 --> 00:14:04,020
Follow me!

151
00:14:04,370 --> 00:14:05,600
The rest of you, attention.

152
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:06,770
Take the machine guns
and occupy the high ground

153
00:14:06,770 --> 00:14:07,900
to set up crossfire.

154
00:14:07,910 --> 00:14:09,620
Do not fire without my order!

155
00:14:09,640 --> 00:14:10,480
Yes, sir!

156
00:14:10,920 --> 00:14:11,920
Go!

157
00:15:44,750 --> 00:15:45,540
Fire!

158
00:16:58,290 --> 00:16:59,530
Ten thousand

159
00:17:00,550 --> 00:17:01,730
heads

160
00:17:02,860 --> 00:17:05,609
must spill

161
00:17:17,130 --> 00:17:18,609
to restore

162
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:21,440
the world's

163
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:24,480
balance!

164
00:17:48,440 --> 00:17:49,750
Get ready for artillery!

165
00:17:49,750 --> 00:17:50,440
Go!

166
00:17:56,490 --> 00:17:57,830
Get out of the way!

167
00:17:58,120 --> 00:17:59,610
Move quickly!

168
00:17:59,680 --> 00:18:01,330
Take cover! Quick!

169
00:18:01,680 --> 00:18:02,790
Go!

170
00:18:06,500 --> 00:18:08,190
Take cover! Quick!

171
00:18:49,710 --> 00:18:51,090
This way! Go!

172
00:18:50,630 --> 00:18:52,680
[Blessings]

173
00:18:51,120 --> 00:18:52,160
Go!

174
00:18:56,460 --> 00:18:57,490
Kong Erbao,

175
00:18:57,930 --> 00:18:58,810
come out!

176
00:18:59,830 --> 00:19:00,780
Run!

177
00:19:45,310 --> 00:19:46,440
Brigade Commander!

178
00:19:46,850 --> 00:19:47,980
Brigade Commander!

179
00:19:55,030 --> 00:19:56,350
How many combatants are left?

180
00:19:56,350 --> 00:19:57,400
Brigade Commander,

181
00:19:57,400 --> 00:19:58,400
they are all here.

182
00:19:58,510 --> 00:19:59,400
Gather ammunition.

183
00:19:59,400 --> 00:20:00,920
The Japanese will attack again soon.

184
00:20:00,920 --> 00:20:01,790
Get ready for battle!

185
00:20:01,790 --> 00:20:02,510
Yes, sir!

186
00:20:03,030 --> 00:20:03,720
Gather ammunition!

187
00:20:03,720 --> 00:20:04,920
-Yes, sir!
-Yes, sir!

188
00:20:12,870 --> 00:20:14,230
Gas shells!

189
00:20:14,260 --> 00:20:15,720
Cover your mouth and nose!

190
00:21:22,820 --> 00:21:23,620
Huang Ziming.

191
00:21:23,910 --> 00:21:24,670
Yes, sir!

192
00:21:24,830 --> 00:21:26,370
Go gather ammunition, the more the better.

193
00:21:26,370 --> 00:21:27,160
Yes, sir!

194
00:21:29,030 --> 00:21:29,840
Adjutant Zhao.

195
00:21:29,840 --> 00:21:30,560
Yes, sir!

196
00:21:32,160 --> 00:21:33,730
Take my sword and last will,

197
00:21:34,070 --> 00:21:35,250
report the situation here
to Division Commander Sun Huaiyi

198
00:21:35,250 --> 00:21:37,380
at Guangyuan Division Headquarters.

199
00:21:39,140 --> 00:21:39,900
Go quickly.

200
00:21:40,180 --> 00:21:41,420
This is an order!

201
00:21:41,440 --> 00:21:42,840
Yes, Brigade Commander!

202
00:21:57,360 --> 00:21:58,740
Keep formation!

203
00:23:17,350 --> 00:23:18,550
Kill!

204
00:23:18,620 --> 00:23:21,190
Kill!

205
00:23:21,790 --> 00:23:23,750
Kill!

206
00:26:15,310 --> 00:26:16,440
Brigade Commander.

207
00:26:17,990 --> 00:26:19,150
You're still alive.

208
00:26:21,030 --> 00:26:22,020
Yes.

209
00:26:22,360 --> 00:26:24,270
Blindy Huang is dead.

210
00:26:28,640 --> 00:26:30,920
Adjutant Zhao is dead too.

211
00:26:33,700 --> 00:26:35,090
They were all real men.

212
00:26:39,020 --> 00:26:39,900
You are too.

213
00:26:42,620 --> 00:26:44,100
I am not.

214
00:26:47,270 --> 00:26:50,680
They are all dead.

215
00:26:53,240 --> 00:26:54,370
Brigade Commander,

216
00:26:54,860 --> 00:26:55,970
let me carry you.

217
00:26:56,640 --> 00:26:57,570
Let me carry you.

218
00:26:58,960 --> 00:26:59,660
We will

219
00:27:00,310 --> 00:27:01,480
run together.

220
00:27:01,750 --> 00:27:03,240
Erbao.

221
00:27:06,840 --> 00:27:07,950
I have to die here.

222
00:27:12,270 --> 00:27:15,160
What is more important than living?

223
00:27:15,300 --> 00:27:17,100
Take this sword

224
00:27:17,590 --> 00:27:18,750
to Nanjing,

225
00:27:19,160 --> 00:27:21,200
No. 99 Yihe Road,

226
00:27:22,070 --> 00:27:23,640
and give it to my father,

227
00:27:24,160 --> 00:27:25,310
Zhang Ruxian.

228
00:27:25,880 --> 00:27:26,880
Tell him

229
00:27:27,090 --> 00:27:28,880
his son Zhang Yunkui

230
00:27:30,530 --> 00:27:32,210
died loyal to his country.

231
00:27:35,920 --> 00:27:38,120
Repeat what I just said.

232
00:27:38,370 --> 00:27:39,330
Nanjing,

233
00:27:39,880 --> 00:27:40,880
No. 99

234
00:27:42,150 --> 00:27:43,250
Yihe Road,

235
00:27:44,810 --> 00:27:46,130
Zhang Ruxian.

236
00:27:46,730 --> 00:27:47,680
Swear.

237
00:27:48,370 --> 00:27:50,500
I have been an orphan since childhood.

238
00:27:51,400 --> 00:27:52,590
I swear on my wife.

239
00:27:53,070 --> 00:27:54,270
If I can't deliver it,

240
00:27:55,310 --> 00:27:55,960
she

241
00:27:56,160 --> 00:27:57,620
will follow someone else.

242
00:28:01,140 --> 00:28:01,900
Go.

243
00:28:04,750 --> 00:28:08,200
Why do you have to die, Brigade Commander?

244
00:28:08,240 --> 00:28:09,270
Don't cry.

245
00:28:11,790 --> 00:28:12,670
Where is he?

246
00:28:13,020 --> 00:28:13,550
On the right!

247
00:28:13,550 --> 00:28:14,790
I'll cover you.

248
00:28:15,700 --> 00:28:17,060
Run outside the town.

249
00:28:17,490 --> 00:28:19,490
Don't look back, just keep running.

250
00:28:19,830 --> 00:28:21,920
This is an order.

251
00:28:23,770 --> 00:28:24,570
Go!

252
00:28:31,850 --> 00:28:32,740
Erbao,

253
00:28:38,680 --> 00:28:40,610
if you're going to live, live well.

254
00:28:42,190 --> 00:28:43,320
Live unyieldingly.

255
