00:33:15,780 --> 00:33:18,590
♪ Like cloud-veiled moon
the thousand-mile Plain disappears ♪

293
00:33:19,420 --> 00:33:20,820
♪ Should youthful heads ♪

294
00:33:21,560 --> 00:33:25,300
♪ In vain turn grey ♪

295
00:33:26,190 --> 00:33:31,400
♪ We would regret for aye ♪

296
00:33:34,600 --> 00:33:35,680
Yueming,

297
00:33:35,830 --> 00:33:37,310
you will surely shed tears
for the sacrifices

298
00:33:37,310 --> 00:33:39,840
the Chinese people made in the battle,

299
00:33:39,940 --> 00:33:43,460
but Mom must tell you the true history.

300
00:33:44,610 --> 00:33:46,120
Their sacrifices

301
00:33:46,150 --> 00:33:48,620
did not reverse the passivity of the war.

302
00:33:48,830 --> 00:33:50,000
Due to the Nationalist Government's

303
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:52,200
fatal flaws at the strategic level

304
00:33:52,200 --> 00:33:54,720
and the extreme chaos
in the command system,

305
00:33:55,060 --> 00:33:58,540
such sacrifices occurred again and again.

306
00:33:59,240 --> 00:34:01,620
Although they inflicted real resistance

307
00:34:01,650 --> 00:34:03,270
and significant losses
on the Japanese Army,

308
00:34:03,270 --> 00:34:06,320
in the end, we still lost Shanghai.

309
00:34:07,000 --> 00:34:08,960
It would take many years before I

310
00:34:08,960 --> 00:34:12,030
could understand
the true nature of this war,

311
00:34:12,030 --> 00:34:15,139
before she could understand why we lost

312
00:34:15,170 --> 00:34:18,290
and how we might have won.

313
00:34:18,440 --> 00:34:19,190
Hello.

314
00:34:19,540 --> 00:34:20,580
Excuse me,

315
00:34:20,960 --> 00:34:22,030
where is this place?

316
00:34:22,030 --> 00:34:23,320
We don't know either.

317
00:34:24,280 --> 00:34:25,080
Thank you.

318
00:34:48,360 --> 00:34:49,150
Sir.

319
00:34:49,360 --> 00:34:50,360
Excuse me,

320
00:34:51,510 --> 00:34:52,280
do you know

321
00:34:52,510 --> 00:34:53,489
where this is?

322
00:34:53,760 --> 00:34:55,190
This is Wuxi.

323
00:34:55,320 --> 00:34:56,280
Wuxi?

324
00:34:58,360 --> 00:35:01,590
Then do you know how to get to Wuhan?

325
00:35:01,820 --> 00:35:02,740
Wuhan?

326
00:35:03,950 --> 00:35:04,770
Go that way.

327
00:35:05,440 --> 00:35:07,070
That way leads to Taicang Port.

328
00:35:07,070 --> 00:35:08,550
There are ships to Wuhan.

329
00:35:10,240 --> 00:35:11,470
What about Nanjing?

330
00:35:11,580 --> 00:35:12,270
Nanjing?

331
00:35:12,800 --> 00:35:13,700
Go this way.

332
00:35:13,960 --> 00:35:17,420
Heading to the train station
is the direction toward Nanjing.

333
00:35:21,510 --> 00:35:23,570
Little brother, you must be thirsty.

334
00:35:24,230 --> 00:35:25,230
Drink some water.

335
00:35:27,880 --> 00:35:29,960
Thank you.

336
00:35:36,030 --> 00:35:37,590
Thank you.

337
00:35:37,610 --> 00:35:38,690
Thank you, sir.

338
00:36:01,760 --> 00:36:03,200
Liu Town.

339
00:36:04,040 --> 00:36:05,770
Which direction is Liu Town?

340
00:36:06,920 --> 00:36:08,980
The Brigade Commander is in Liu Town.

341
00:36:21,100 --> 00:36:22,230
Brigade Commander.

342
00:36:22,710 --> 00:36:23,460
Well,

343
00:36:23,590 --> 00:36:24,110
Nan...

344
00:36:25,320 --> 00:36:27,140
I have to go to Nanjing,

345
00:36:27,960 --> 00:36:28,920
but

346
00:36:30,510 --> 00:36:32,930
I definitely need to go to Wuhan first.

347
00:36:33,110 --> 00:36:35,140
I have to find Xiaoyue first.

348
00:36:35,320 --> 00:36:36,580
Then I'll go to Nanjing

349
00:36:36,710 --> 00:36:39,590
to deliver the sword
to your father, okay?

350
00:36:41,790 --> 00:36:42,590
Don't worry.

351
00:36:45,220 --> 00:36:47,020
I will definitely go to Nanjing.

352
00:37:20,670 --> 00:37:21,360
Wait,

353
00:37:22,070 --> 00:37:23,200
Brigade Commander,

354
00:37:23,220 --> 00:37:24,820
are you really following me?

355
00:37:24,950 --> 00:37:25,790
I...

356
00:37:27,110 --> 00:37:29,300
I'm just a lowly worm.

357
00:37:29,440 --> 00:37:31,000
Please, spare me!

358
00:37:31,020 --> 00:37:31,620
I...

359
00:37:32,110 --> 00:37:34,030
I have to go to Wuhan.

360
00:38:09,580 --> 00:38:13,010
[Nanjing]

361
00:38:12,970 --> 00:38:14,110
Great-grandfather!

362
00:38:14,110 --> 00:38:15,070
Madam!

363
00:38:16,560 --> 00:38:17,670
Great-grandfather!

364
00:38:17,670 --> 00:38:18,670
Any new battle reports?

365
00:38:18,670 --> 00:38:20,280
No new reports yet.

366
00:38:20,670 --> 00:38:23,320
I saw Deputy Division Commander Liao
on the way.

367
00:38:23,320 --> 00:38:25,180
Liao Fengnian is back in Nanjing?

368
00:38:26,110 --> 00:38:26,880
Father,

369
00:38:27,230 --> 00:38:29,160
does that mean Yunkui is also back?

370
00:38:32,590 --> 00:38:33,680
I'll go ask him.

371
00:38:34,360 --> 00:38:35,190
Get my clothes.

372
00:38:35,190 --> 00:38:35,880
Yes.

373
00:38:48,630 --> 00:38:49,550
Mrs. Liu,

374
00:38:50,320 --> 00:38:51,770
Liao Fengnian is back in Nanjing.

375
00:38:51,770 --> 00:38:53,430
Yunkui should be back too.

376
00:38:53,590 --> 00:38:55,390
The young master is coming back?

377
00:38:55,590 --> 00:38:56,590
That's great.

378
00:38:57,110 --> 00:38:59,640
Just in time for some
duck blood vermicelli soup.

379
00:38:59,640 --> 00:39:01,080
Is it the batch I made?

380
00:39:02,550 --> 00:39:03,980
Who else would it be?

381
00:39:04,190 --> 00:39:05,320
Look at the noodles—

382
00:39:05,440 --> 00:39:06,640
some are thick,

383
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:08,510
some are thin, all crooked.

384
00:39:08,510 --> 00:39:09,480
It's so ugly.

385
00:39:10,070 --> 00:39:11,340
It looks fine to me.

386
00:39:11,360 --> 00:39:12,320
Let me do it.

387
00:39:13,150 --> 00:39:14,190
Be careful.

388
00:39:15,210 --> 00:39:20,800
[Nationalist Government]

389
00:39:33,670 --> 00:39:37,330
[Nationalist Government]

390
00:40:08,200 --> 00:40:14,550
[Nationalist Government]

391
00:40:08,880 --> 00:40:11,400
The Nationalist Government.

392
00:40:11,440 --> 00:40:12,510
So big.

393
00:40:14,620 --> 00:40:17,800
[[Zhang's Mansion]]

394
00:40:17,840 --> 00:40:23,500
[[Understanding Water, Honoring Mountain]]

395
00:40:30,930 --> 00:40:33,400
[No. 99, Yihe Road]

396
00:40:35,830 --> 00:40:36,710
Madam,

397
00:40:36,840 --> 00:40:37,900
I have to say,

398
00:40:38,000 --> 00:40:39,000
your hands

399
00:40:39,020 --> 00:40:41,030
are meant for embroidery and writing.

400
00:40:41,030 --> 00:40:43,210
I should be the one doing this.

401
00:40:45,440 --> 00:40:46,510
Sour liquid.

402
00:40:46,540 --> 00:40:47,550
How many times have I told you?

403
00:40:47,550 --> 00:40:48,800
You just can't remember.

404
00:40:48,800 --> 00:40:49,510
The jar failed—starch didn't settle.

405
00:40:49,510 --> 00:40:51,110
Look, it's all sticking together.

406
00:40:51,110 --> 00:40:52,320
Just pull it apart.

407
00:40:52,320 --> 00:40:53,760
I think it's fine.

408
00:40:54,360 --> 00:40:56,690
You should listen to the elders.

409
00:40:56,880 --> 00:40:58,840
This is the method
my grandmother taught me.

410
00:40:58,840 --> 00:41:00,840
Once it goes in the pot,
it'll all stick together

411
00:41:00,840 --> 00:41:01,510
in a lump.

412
00:41:01,550 --> 00:41:03,750
Won't it separate when you boil it?

413
00:41:03,880 --> 00:41:04,880
Besides,

414
00:41:04,960 --> 00:41:07,110
it doesn't matter if you like it or not.

415
00:41:07,150 --> 00:41:08,610
As long as Yunkui likes it.

416
00:41:10,760 --> 00:41:11,800
You're asking for trouble!

417
00:41:11,800 --> 00:41:12,550
Who let you in?

418
00:41:12,550 --> 00:41:14,290
Quick, quick, get out!

419
00:41:14,710 --> 00:41:15,440
Mrs. Liu,

420
00:41:17,510 --> 00:41:18,920
are there any potstickers left?

421
00:41:18,920 --> 00:41:19,670
Yes.

422
00:41:20,000 --> 00:41:20,730
Go pack some.

423
00:41:23,840 --> 00:41:24,480
Wait outside.

424
00:41:24,480 --> 00:41:25,750
I'll get them for you.

425
00:41:25,960 --> 00:41:27,280
I'm not a beggar.

426
00:41:31,510 --> 00:41:32,590
What are you doing?

427
00:41:36,710 --> 00:41:39,970
I'm here to deliver a message
for Brigade Commander Zhang.

428
00:41:44,460 --> 00:41:46,150
The 87th Brigade?

429
00:41:46,360 --> 00:41:47,160
Yes.

430
00:41:47,210 --> 00:41:48,670
I'm from the 87th Brigade.

431
00:41:48,960 --> 00:41:50,420
Our young master is
your Brigade Commander.

432
00:41:50,420 --> 00:41:51,940
This is his wife.

433
00:41:53,680 --> 00:41:54,630
Madam.

434
00:42:01,400 --> 00:42:01,970
You...

435
00:42:02,920 --> 00:42:03,710
You came...

436
00:42:06,960 --> 00:42:08,000
Where is Yunkui?

437
00:42:09,170 --> 00:42:10,440
Isn't he back?

438
00:42:15,110 --> 00:42:16,640
Is Old Master Zhang at home?

439
00:42:16,920 --> 00:42:18,250
Our Brigade Commander ordered

440
00:42:18,250 --> 00:42:20,380
that I can only speak to the Old Master.

441
00:42:25,840 --> 00:42:26,760
He went out.

442
00:42:26,780 --> 00:42:28,190
You can tell me, it's okay.

443
00:42:28,190 --> 00:42:29,440
Yes, it's okay.

444
00:42:29,550 --> 00:42:30,380
No.

445
00:42:30,670 --> 00:42:31,540
It's an order.

446
00:42:31,960 --> 00:42:33,820
I can only speak to the Old Master.

447
00:42:35,750 --> 00:42:36,830
Okay.

448
00:42:39,230 --> 00:42:40,070
Mrs. Liu,

449
00:42:40,280 --> 00:42:41,480
go make some hot food.

450
00:42:42,960 --> 00:42:43,800
Wait a moment.

451
00:42:43,840 --> 00:42:44,920
Duck blood vermicelli soup.

452
00:42:44,920 --> 00:42:46,030
Okay, got it.

453
00:42:49,710 --> 00:42:50,630
Young man,

454
00:42:50,960 --> 00:42:52,230
don't stand outside.

455
00:42:52,440 --> 00:42:53,440
Come in and rest.

456
00:42:53,460 --> 00:42:54,500
Follow me.

457
00:42:55,770 --> 00:42:56,640
Madam.,

458
00:42:57,030 --> 00:42:58,570
I won't go in.

459
00:42:58,630 --> 00:42:59,500
I...

460
00:43:00,510 --> 00:43:02,000
I'll just wait in the courtyard.
